name: WhisperSRTube
description: A subtitling tool I made because I found Youtube's current auto-translation and captioning to be temperamental at best. Built with Python on Tkinter.

name: EDA-Ottawa-Traffic
description: Nokia EDA (Event Driven Automation) platform enables its users to get real-time data w/o configuring any networking infrastructure. I am exploring the playground EDA toolkit filtering public Ottawa traffic data flows into a stack powered by Azure data processing services to visualize on Grafana.
